_:Nacd8b2545b52476ca25e2500804e6dca <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Paul Maynard was Parliamentary Under Secretary of State at the Department for Work and Pensions from 13 November 2023 to 5 July 2024.</p>\n\n<p>He was Parliamentary Under Secretary of State at the Department for Transport between July 2019 and February 2020.</p>\n\n<p>He was also Parliamentary Under Secretary of State at the Ministry of Justice between May 2019 and July 2019.</p>\n\n<p>He was previously Government Whip (Lord Commissioner of HM Treasury). Paul was Parliamentary Under Secretary of State at the Department for Transport from July 2016 to January 2018. He was Conservative MP for Blackpool North and Cleveleys from 2010 to 2024.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"education\">Education</h2>\n\n<p>Paul was educated at St Ambrose College, Altrincham and University College, Oxford where he studied history.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"career-outside-politics\">Career outside politics</h2>\n\n<p>Before entering Parliament, Paul worked as a political adviser and speechwriter.</p>\n" .
_:N6df7f48622a64603bf9617a7a9b5cd3c <http://schema.org/position> "1"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#integer> .
